item.title: UCSC AI at NeurIPS and EMNLP 2023
item.description: The UCSC AI Group will be at NeurIPS and EMNLP 2023! NeurIPS Attending: Prof. Wang, Prof. Gilpin, Prof. Marinescu, Prof. Zhang, Prof. Xie, and Prof. Zhou. Main conference: Photoswap: Personalized Subject Swapping in Images. Jing Gu, Yilin Wang, Nanxuan Zhao, Tsu-Jui Fu, Wei Xiong, Qing Liu, Zhifei Zhang, He Zhang, Jianming Zhang, HyunJoon Jung, Xin Eric Wang . Th, Dec 14, 08:45 – Poster Session 5 LayoutGPT: Compositional Visual Planning and Generation with Large Language Models.
